company_name: FRIEDRICH KORNFEIND, GEFLUGEL - WILD UND EIER WIEN XII., BISCHOFFGASSE 20
information: The company FRIEDRICH KORNFEIND, GEFLUGEL - WILD UND EIER WIEN XII., BISCHOFFGASSE 20, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1895, which operates in the Poultry, rabbits and game - farming industry. It is based in Wien, Austria.
